  "instructions": [
    "Heat butter in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add onion and garlic and cook until softened, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add carrots, green beans, and salt. Cook for 4 minutes, or until vegetables start to tenderize.",
    "Add white rice and stir to coat with butter and mix with vegetables.",
    "Pour in water and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low, cover, and simmer for 15 minutes, or until rice is tender and liquid is absorbed.",
    "Stir in tabasco sauce and black pepper.",
    "Fluff with a fork and garnish with parsley.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!"
